       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DRIVECLM.
       AUTHOR. OPENAI.
       REMARKS. DRIVER FOR INTEGRATION TESTS — CALLS CLMADJ001.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY POLDATA.
       01  LK-CLAIM-STATUS          PIC X.
           88 LK-CLAIM-APPROVED     VALUE 'A'.
           88 LK-CLAIM-REJECTED     VALUE 'R'.
           88 LK-CLAIM-PENDING      VALUE 'P'.
       01  RPT-LINE                 PIC X(140).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN.
           PERFORM SEED-CLM-APPROVE
           CALL "CLMADJ001" USING WS-POLICY-MASTER-REC
                                   LK-CLAIM-STATUS
           STRING "CLM_OK|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  LK-CLAIM-STATUS DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-CLAIM-DECISION DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-RETURN-CODE DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-CLAIM-PAYMENT-AMOUNT DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-CONTRACT-STATUS DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  INTO RPT-LINE
           END-STRING
           DISPLAY FUNCTION TRIM(RPT-LINE TRAILING)
           STOP RUN.

       SEED-CLM-APPROVE.
           INITIALIZE WS-POLICY-MASTER-REC
           MOVE 20200615 TO PM-PROCESS-DATE
           MOVE "T1001" TO PM-PLAN-CODE
           MOVE "AC" TO PM-CONTRACT-STATUS
           MOVE 20180101 TO PM-ISSUE-DATE
                                 PM-EFFECTIVE-DATE
           MOVE 20200501 TO PM-PAID-TO-DATE
           MOVE 20280101 TO PM-EXPIRY-DATE
           MOVE 10000000000.00 TO PM-SUM-ASSURED
           MOVE 5000.00 TO PM-MODAL-PREMIUM
           MOVE ZERO TO PM-RIDER-COUNT PM-POLICY-LOAN-BALANCE
           MOVE "CD" TO PM-CLAIM-TYPE
           MOVE "NAT" TO PM-CAUSE-OF-DEATH
           MOVE "CLMTEST000001" TO PM-CLAIM-ID
           MOVE 20200301 TO PM-DATE-OF-DEATH
           MOVE "BENEFICIARY ONE" TO PM-BENEFICIARY-NAME
           MOVE "Y" TO PM-CLAIM-DOC-DEATH-CERT
                         PM-CLAIM-DOC-CLAIM-FORM
                         PM-CLAIM-DOC-ID-PROOF
                         PM-CLAIM-DOC-MEDICAL
           MOVE "P" TO LK-CLAIM-STATUS
           .
